_Control/Marco_Integrado_de_Cont_Int_leyen.pdf\"><img src=\"../uploads/176_Marco_Integrado_de_Control/Marco_Integrado_de_Control_Interno.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"151\" height=\"167\" /></a></p>',NULL,NULL,'2015-07-19 00:00:00',3,12376,1,0,0,30,NULL,0,1,NULL,'[{\"Type\":\"title\",\"Value\":\"Marco Integrado de Control\",\"Preview\":\"<title>Marco Integrado de Control</title>\"},{\"Type\":\"language\",\"Value\":\"es-MX\",\"Preview\":\"<meta http-equiv=\\\"Content-Language\\\" content=\\\"es-MX\\\"/>\"},{\"Type\":\"description\",\"Value\":\"Marco Integrado de Control&nbsp;\",\"Preview\":\"<meta name=\\\"description\\\" content=\\\"Marco Integrado de Control&nbsp;\\\" />\"}]',0),(178,1,61,'178_SAAR','SAAR','2015-07-21 00:00:00','2016-06-13 12:22:41','2015-07-17 00:00:00',0,'<h2><strong>Sistema Automatizado para la Administraci&oacute;n de Riesgos</strong></h2>\r\n<div>\r\n<p><strong>Objetivo. </strong>Automatizar el desarrollo del proceso general de administraci&oacute;n de riesgos en las instituciones del sector p&uacute;blico, con el prop&oacute;sito de que identifiquen, eval&uacute;en, prioricen,&nbsp;respondan y supervisen adecuadamente los riesgos, incluidos los de corrupci&oacute;n, que en caso de materializarse afecten de forma adversa el logro de&nbsp;los objetivos institucionales.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><strong><a href=\"../uploads/178_SAAR/SAAR_2_0_08062016.zip\"><img src=\"../uploads/178_SAAR/01_Sistem_autom_SAAR_Excel.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"164\" height=\"163\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"../uploads/178_SAAR/MANUAL_SAAR.pdf\"><img src=\"../uploads/178_SAAR/02_Manual_sist_aut_admin_riesf.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"147\" height=\"154\" /></a><br /></strong></p>',NULL,NULL,'2015-07-19 00:00:00',3,12241,1,0,0,30,NULL,0,1,NULL,'[{\"Type\":\"title\",\"Value\":\"SAAR\",\"Preview\":\"<title>SAAR</title>\"},{\"Type\":\"language\",\"Value\":\"es-MX\",\"Preview\":\"<meta http-equiv=\\\"Content-Language\\\" content=\\\"es-MX\\\"/>\"},{\"Type\":\"description\",\"Value\":\"Sistema Autom